      "commentBody": "### TTS and STT endpoints missing authentication error handling\n\n**Medium Severity**\n\n<!-- DESCRIPTION START -->\nThe `/api/v1/voice/tts` and `/api/v1/voice/stt` endpoints are missing authentication error handling present in all other new voice endpoints. When `requireAuthOrApiKeyWithOrg` throws errors like \"Invalid or expired API key\" or \"API key is inactive\", these endpoints return a generic 500 error (\"Failed to generate speech\" / \"Failed to transcribe audio\") instead of a proper 401 response. Developers using invalid API keys receive misleading server error messages instead of clear authentication failure responses.\n<!-- DESCRIPTION END -->\n\n<!-- BUGBOT_BUG_ID: ref1_5b1022f8-fcbe-4015-862a-0fa6bde471d7 -->\n\n<!-- LOCATIONS START\napp/api/v1/voice/tts/route.ts#L200-L248\napp/api/v1/voice/stt/route.ts#L246-L307\nLOCATIONS END -->\n<details>\n<summary>Additional Locations (1)</summary>\n\n- [`app/api/v1/voice/stt/route.ts#L246-L307`](https://github.com/elizaOS/eliza-cloud-v2/blob/797743798b2713dc487f80b9e42f9620dcd11c48/app/api/v1/voice/stt/route.ts#L246-L307)\n\n</details>\n\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/open?data=eyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCIsImtpZCI6ImJ1Z2JvdC12MiJ9..vjwXdyNXvL0H6y1BD9LkUZoG08DpfyWrqifh-0t2M5VljbLYRYb9uOYsinv0wxFL51bPStsKmk3gB4SqFTIVN_OQWtrCeARKObtamdPEpw-98WXdNgkRz3dBLPEzWg6lyF8vM9TBsr8JuDwVZf6YysA7Nq9AOT0t11Dvp6IQk38hp-0LVbhXCxj70AXzOd1eA2xJZSTmO4qOAtwzT9ZpaPaipQCwZ6tDW9Pdj-Rn3fIIiYopNlpU2yhK7f3f-Jp_RedBdx1TRnGMyesWRhCU0MBK4nkyZE1-kooG5t0_Hf3sHkJnHQTxamT_3QBwlZnvIpxkp87vBJFTy11aZ0Um1g\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-light.png\"><img alt=\"Fix in Cursor\" width=\"115\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-dark.png\"></picture></a>&nb