      "commentBody": "### Duplicated auth error checking pattern\n\n**Low Severity**\n\n<!-- DESCRIPTION START -->\nThe `isAuthError` check logic is duplicated between `handleGET` (lines 95-98) and `handlePUT` (lines 179-182). Extract this pattern to a helper function like `isAuthenticationError(message: string): boolean` at the module level or in a shared utility.\n<!-- DESCRIPTION END -->\n\n<!-- BUGBOT_BUG_ID: cq_85ca14d9-4827-4f13-b2db-efd7724e6f73 -->\n\n<!-- LOCATIONS START\napp/api/v1/billing/settings/route.ts#L94-L98\nLOCATIONS END -->\n<a href=\"https://cursor.com/open?data=eyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCIsImtpZCI6ImJ1Z2JvdC12MiJ9..bwoq1ttKaj5JDAjUAh7iu3s5_viA5jeM6mkgCeR2QngK09txKMdfBneuNX9DGCeQCI4oNqWwcvXT8rePKhQDCZzdecnd1QxIp5EJu9h_S8-87nfzrQTVCQE11CctMq4_W_yMzm8R1SIOoly7duPF6TkOlcSNa0uKCYdGLoh7uakHoQpl2THqCqDS1wer7y5YsqN3NOwxmg-FbYtrCnSzBYEnjAk8Lw2SWFqsOeZUqfOXKVDfF9AF3yniK37yMsdgmSWfOw2LaI3XOB1igOOvHfjrAW-rOjKnN1eqrOhqHaC3vuB90iGWG3mqgBCWZbPg8BJcXQ2tA_XfkKOLDsr_ZQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-light.png\"><img alt=\"Fix in Cursor\" width=\"115\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-dark.png\"></picture></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?data=eyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCIsImtpZCI6ImJ1Z2JvdC12MiJ9..vsNWId87Yumn8m4xZwv8pr8JA70q8C1q2I90jVYblrpeXzewTWdQUxWOMNef43B05ZRQRxVuKQWgd1QexUPxiEAqWcpt9-T26RQMQ0UdpSoi0RUSTJHqfzHFnhJc7BDtYr17VadzmdsiVXlIKhFEnSWo4naup-qaddOVD8XgZzUOxJRHhP7lL7oMQvQo_O-tM8J-7bjGxk5Z_ff--ZMNOLEJnjPdYuD6towVKrsKl2CvNZOSwFlFpqvCAkn94EWE2L3IY6mVd5UyZsTdMSCuxZX2CHqQlZtO3af9O_jXkiI8FzlngmXowSMGOPPbD5fBXrTP_edKiggAgHdWlDduBQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/a